{"tid":985342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一分鐘前有冇人feel到地震左一下","createTime":"2019-01-17T13:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T16:07:42.000Z","uid":37458,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"310cae799dafc76ce18f3bf6667162db8a55e510","tid":985342,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"9:29-9:30左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8f0dcda5f974576fa5f17ad02d71b87e9dd40a","tid":985342,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797454cf0e05f8c2c85571d6a80b1ee2d9fc99e7","tid":985342,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"邊區呀"},{"pid":"642b749f0407ab4b9e93d25923d43ca6f9a50d11","tid":985342,"uid":43428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"有呀 我成個人震到跌落床"},{"pid":"3a93bc01933a9573b6f891504d4651828571543e","tid":985342,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797454cf0e05f8c2c85571d6a80b1ee2d9fc99e7","tid":985342,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"邊區呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"北區"},{"pid":"50174083142d950928117591fcf50d44a273af96","tid":985342,"uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3a93bc01933a9573b6f891504d4651828571543e","tid":985342,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797454cf0e05f8c2c85571d6a80b1ee2d9fc99e7","tid":985342,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"邊區呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"北區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"聽講今日欣宜去咗個頭"},{"pid":"943b04e186d89103ac82cca1fbb97eb779c14aa9","tid":985342,"uid":54824,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=129169&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D129169%26section_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D8&d=D1Y0%2Fdp%2BO8vcwf99EFFcLI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=43494f0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D129169%26section_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D8&h=34a3b3b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=129169&amp;section_name=wtt&amp;kw=8</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳地震帶伸延至港<br />\n港大教授：毋須過份擔心<br />\n2010-11-12<br />\n<br />\n人稱香港是「福地」，除了颱風暴雨，鮮有其他天然災害。但深圳市地震局最近一份報告引起港人關注。該局在報告中稱，發現三條「中強地震」構造背景的地震斷裂帶，其中一條蓮塘斷裂帶更伸延至香港。香港大學地球科學系教授陳龍生指，蓮塘斷裂帶地震周期長，難以預測地震發生的時間、強度，但本港過往發生的地震都是一、二級的「小兒科」，市民毋須對這地震斷裂帶「南下」過份擔心。<br />\n<br />\n        蓮塘斷裂帶由福田南一帶起向西南延伸，經過鹽田坳、西坑、高坳東、田螺坑、求水嶺、蓮塘、西嶺下村、羅芳村後，進入香港深圳河一帶地區，包括打鼓嶺、文錦渡，落馬洲。若發生「勁」級數地震，如五級以上，上水亦會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n        中國地震局駐深圳辦事處副主任劉昇禮說，斷裂帶只有發生地震的「潛在危險」，又指過去深圳只受到周邊地區地震的輕微影響，未有破壞性損壞，地震活動相對穩定，但地震難以預測，因此亦要戒備。<br />\n<br />\n        「<br />\n潛在危險」難以預測，老老實實，香港究竟會否發生大地震？要拆解這個驚心疑問，首先要了解何謂斷裂帶。港大地球科學系教授陳龍生解釋，地球佈滿斷裂帶，而所謂的斷裂帶，是岩石長期受壓，抵受不住造成斷裂，形成斷層，板塊移動得厲害，「噼啪」裂開，就造成地震，「周圍都是斷層，但好多都好老、不活躍，無地震紀錄。」<br />\n<br />\n        陳指出，預測地震，通常根據過往紀錄，計算地震周期，像加拿大、日本這些國家，地震頻率高，容易作預測，相反地震活動愈少，掌握資料不多，就愈難預測發作周期，「如果從來無發生地震，一旦發生，威力會好大。」"},{"pid":"91f0ea29bf5d6fd3b59047a7bfc04035a795f2b2","tid":985342,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310cae799dafc76ce18f3bf6667162db8a55e510","tid":985342,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"9:29-9:30左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weather.gov.hk/gts/equake/quake-info_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin